没有图像或数据丢失。我们修复了该错误，该问题将在未来几天内得到完全解决。</p> — 支持 (@Support) <a href="https://twitter.com/Support/status/1693732980324536695?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 21 日</a></blockquote></div><p>X 没有回应评论请求，也没有提供有关错误原因的更多详细信息。该公司表示，它没有丢失底层图像或数据。但这并不是过去几个月里该服务的某些方面第一次受到干扰。由于<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/every-link-on-twitter-is-broken-right-now-165929931.html"><ins>API 更改</ins></a>，该平台上的照片和链接在 3 月份曾短暂中断。该公司最近还被发现<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/x-is-slowing-down-links-to-websites-elon-musk-has-publicly-feuded-with-185544463.html"><ins>放慢了</ins></a>与埃隆·马斯克此前攻击过的一些竞争对手和其他实体运营的网站的链接速度。马斯克曾多次抱怨X基础设施的状况，但也大幅<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/musk-orders-twitter-cut-infrastructure-costs-by-1-bln-sources-2022-11-03/"><ins>削减了</ins></a>服务器预算，并解雇了许多站点可靠性工程师，以降低成本。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/x-is-fixing-a-bug-that-wiped-out-twitter-images-from-before-2014-224746265.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/x-is-fixing-a-bug-that-wiped-out-twitter-images-from-before-2014-224746265.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d1d73052-a4c6-478e-b9e6-343a3b9678ce</guid><dc:creator>卡丽莎·贝尔</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 21 Aug 2023 22:47:46 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692658067</ingested><modified> 2023-08-21T22:47:52+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Celebrities]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Karissa Bell]]></category><media:content height="3306" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/cf025f80-4073-11ee-bef9-2c5b0705c510" width="4959"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3306" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/cf025f80-4073-11ee-bef9-2c5b0705c510" width="4959"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[SOPA Images via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[CHINA - 2023/08/09: In this photo illustration, the logo of the social network "X" (formerly: Twitter) is displayed in the Apple App Store. (Photo Illustration by Sheldon Cooper/SOPA Images/LightRocket via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[In this photo illustration, the logo of the social network "...]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Webb Space Telescope captures the Ring Nebula in mesmerizing detail]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/james-webb-telescope-marks-first-anniversary-with-an-image-of-a-nearby-stellar-nursery-163444912.html">詹姆斯·韦伯太空望远镜</a>（JWST）捕获了今天<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://esawebb.org/news/weic2320/?lang">发布的</a>非常详细的环形星云图像。气态云也称为 M57 和 NGC 6720，包含 20,000 个富含分子氢的致密球体。它距地球约 2,500 光年。</p><p>第一张图像（上图）是用 NIRCam（近红外相机）拍摄的，它是韦伯太空望远镜的主要传感器之一。它旨在检测近红外光谱中的光，并可以捕获非常详细的图像。 NIRCam 还拍摄了同样令人着迷的创世之柱的<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/james-webb-space-telescope-pillars-of-creation-space-miri-163527776.html">更新图像</a>。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>与此同时，第二张图像（下图）是使用 JWST 的 MIRI（中红外仪器）拍摄的。它更好地突出了星云在其外边缘之外的（大约）十个同心弧，这些弧可能是由其中心恒星与其轨道上的低质量伴星相互作用形成的。欧洲航天局在一份新闻稿中写道：“通过这种方式，像环形星云这样的星云揭示了一种天文考古学，天文学家研究星云以了解创造它的恒星。” </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/367a66d0-4065-11ee-af5a-f075a140568c" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/367a66d0-4065-11ee-af5a-f075a140568c" style="height:768px;width:1280px;" alt="韦伯望远镜拍摄的环形星云的详细图像。这是一个巨大的气体环，外环呈红色，在中心附近逐渐变得更加绿色和蓝色。" data-uuid="218ac239-2290-3c31-9549-e91d9e9c2b60"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> ESA / 韦伯 / NASA / CSA / M. Barlow / N. Cox / R. Wesson</div></figure><p> 1779 年，法国天文学家 Charles Messier 和 Antoine Darquier de Pellepoix 在寻找彗星时偶然发现了环状星云。它是一个行星状星云，之所以如此命名，是因为早期研究人员将它们的外观误认为是遥远的世界。环形星云是由一颗中等大小的恒星形成的，当它耗尽燃料并接近灭亡时，它会脱落外层。</p><p>欧洲航天局写道：“色彩缤纷的主环是由星云中心一颗垂死恒星释放的气体组成的。” “这颗恒星正在成为一颗白矮星——一种非常小、致密且炽热的天体，是像太阳这样的恒星的最后进化阶段。”</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/webb-space-telescope-captures-the-ring-nebula-in-mesmerizing-detail-213005773.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/webb-space-telescope-captures-the-ring-nebula-in-mesmerizing-detail-213005773.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d86ba66a-dc57-4c01-9469-9df807e6e3bb</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 21 Aug 2023 21:30:05 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692653407</ingested><modified> 2023-08-21T21:30:13+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Science]]></category><category><![CDATA[Space & Astronomy]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="2366" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/9acc4690-4064-11ee-9ffb-c95ff7225bcd" width="3943"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2366" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/9acc4690-4064-11ee-9ffb-c95ff7225bcd" width="3943"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ESA/Webb / NASA / CSA / M. Barlow / N. Cox / R. Wesson]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Detailed image of the Ring Nebula, captured by the Webb Telescope. It's an enormous gassy ring with reddish outer rings, which move towards more green and blue near the center.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Ring Nebula]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Cult of the Lamb and Don’t Starve Together team up for a creepy-cute crossover]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>过去几年中最出色的两部独立热门影片是<em>《羔羊崇拜》</em>和<em>《多人版饥荒》。</em>现在，这对广受好评的宠儿正在<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2023/08/21/cult-of-the-lamb-and-dont-starve-together-join-forces/"><ins>联手打造新的游戏模式、</ins></a>独特的游戏内物品，甚至还有一些角色客串。这种交叉对两款游戏都有影响，尽管每种游戏都会获得不同的福利。</p><p>这里最大的吸引力是<em>《羔羊崇拜》</em>的全新游戏模式，其直接灵感来自<em>《多人版饥荒》。</em>恰如其分的“忏悔模式”通过为你的小羊主人公提供与你可爱且<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://cult-of-the-lamb.fandom.com/wiki/Bowl_of_Poop"><ins>痴迷于便便的追随者相同的凡人需求，从而增加了压力因素。</ins></a>换句话说，除了为你的邪教提供食物之外，你还必须自己吃饭和住所。您将获得与<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/engadget-best-games-2022-150020578.html"><ins>广受好评的传统游戏相同的选择，</ins></a>因此您可以吃肉和蔬菜，或者以<em>黄衫队</em>风格（同类相食）。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这些游戏现在还共享一些物品来创造独特的外观，因此您将能够解锁<em>《饥荒》</em>中的<em>《羔羊崇拜》</em>中的装饰，例如棍子上的猪头，反之亦然。寻找新的宝箱皮肤、圣堂装饰品等等。 </p><div id="8a275e8e671c4b64bcc2e91a9936ff46"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XxzXFNCv-UQ" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>最后，有一些角色正在通过“交叉门户”。韦伯来自<em>《饥荒》的巨人统治</em>DLC，现在是一名可解锁的邪教成员，并具有新的“永不饥饿”特征，因此您可以将青草粥留给真正需要的人。此外，由于受其他游戏启发的服装和设计选项， <em>《饥荒》中类似羔羊的</em>电子小动物/宠物变得更加均匀，呃，羔羊。</p><p>该更新现已适用于 PlayStation 和 Xbox 主机。开发者还指出， <em>《羔羊崇拜》</em>即将迎来重大内容更新，《<em>多人版饥荒》</em>将继续在其正在进行的 From Beyond 故事情节中收到更多内容。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/cult-of-the-lamb-and-dont-starve-together-team-up-for-a-creepy-cute-crossover-184518173.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/cult-of-the-lamb-and-dont-starve-together-team-up-for-a-creepy-cute-crossover-184518173.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> abb392e9-e445-4d4a-ab3f-f4a5c670ddbb</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 21 Aug 2023 18:45:18 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692643405</ingested><modified> 2023-08-21T18:43:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1297" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7d3e5630-4051-11ee-a7fe-f26c728bb64e" width="2323"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1297" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7d3e5630-4051-11ee-a7fe-f26c728bb64e" width="2323"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Devolver Digital]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[An ad for the crossover event.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Cult of the Lamb with Don't Starve Together]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best Nintendo Switch games for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>就在五年前，任天堂正处于十字路口。 Wii U 在游戏机大战中排名第三，在承受巨大压力后，该公司开始尝试通过<em>Miitomo</em>和<em>Super Mario Run</em>进军移动游戏领域。快进到今天： <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-switch-oled-review-130025998.html">Switch</a>很可能成为该公司有史以来最畅销的“家用游戏机”，并且有 7 款 Switch<em>游戏的销量</em>超过了 Wii U 游戏机。任天堂的一切即将到来，这要归功于 Switch 独特的混合格式和不断增长的游戏库以及异常强大的第三方支持。</p><p>然而，Switch 的在线商店并不是最容易浏览的，因此本指南旨在帮助新手开始他们的旅程。这些是您目前应该拥有的游戏。我们会定期修改并酌情添加到列表中。哦，如果您有 Switch Lite，请不用担心：便携式游戏机完全支持列表中的每个游戏。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2>动物森友会：新视野</h2><p><core-commerce id="8361a7f46f134267bd4419129b9c3eed" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDdTUjFCUk41P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWRwLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YzllYTc3Ny0yNGMyLTQ0YmUtOTM2ZC1iZDVhNTQ0MzVjY2YifQ&amp;signature=AQAAARSMfKdTVgEk3ja-Ql5O3gEHCgEiR_uH8TLM4tsVHerU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07SR1BRN5"><em>《动物森友会》</em></a>是该系列迄今为止最好的游戏。它简化了早期游戏中的许多笨重方面，并为玩家提供了足够的动力来继续塑造他们的岛屿社区。正如您所期望的，它看起来也比之前的任何条目都要好，让您更有动力去填充您的虚拟家庭和壁橱。声音设计达到令人头晕的 ASMR 舒适度水平。是的，当我们在全球大流行中被困在家里时， <em>《新视野》</em>无疑是一种令人难以置信的舒缓现实的逃避现实的方式。</p><h2>猎天使魔女3 </h2><p><core-commerce id="4843091ad812442bb3ee2cd7bf636f62" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <em>《猎天使魔女 3》</em>对该系列中最荒谬的主题进行了精彩的放大。它沉迷于荒诞，却没有破坏快速的战斗或贝优妮塔无与伦比的时尚感和机智。 <em>《猎天使魔女 3》</em>充满欢乐、机制丰富且充满动作，此外，它还允许玩家变身为真正的地狱列车，以击倒一心摧毁多元宇宙的巨大野兽。贝优妮塔优雅地在战斗中翩翩起舞，前一秒扔下俏皮话，用她的枪鞋射击敌人，下一秒就变成了一只巨大的蜘蛛生物。</p><p> 《猎天使魔女》系列变得越来越怪异，但这并不意味着它正在失去令人满意的游戏玩法。在该系列的第三部中，贝优妮塔强大、自信且有趣。她是一个由巫术松散地结合在一起的宇宙中的变装皇后，这种组合的混乱确实是神奇的。</p><h2>霓虹白</h2><p><core-commerce id="413e30e414b24a4696054b4dadc59955" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>和所有优秀的游戏一样，Neon White 上手简单，但精通却很难。基本要求是你击败关卡中的每一个恶魔并到达终点。它的玩法就像一款快节奏的第一人称射击游戏，其复杂性来自于你的武器，这些卡牌可以开火，也可以用于特殊的移动或攻击能力。真正的挑战来自评分系统，该系统根据您完成一个级别所需的时间对您进行评分。</p><p>游戏关卡不到 100 个，所有关卡都需要学习、重复和完善。尽管它具有第一人称射击游戏的视觉效果，但它更像是《赛道狂飙》和平台游戏的结合体。您很快就会将铜牌变成金牌，然后获得“王牌”，这应该是您的最终目标。然后您会看到在线排行榜，并意识到您已经剩下几秒钟了。<em>然后</em>你会随机获得一个关卡的秘密红色奖章，说“哦不”，然后意识到有一个隐藏的完美层等待你实现。 <em>– 亚伦·索普里斯，执行主编</em></p><h2>帕拉莫玛瞄准镜</h2><p><core-commerce id="c916d0c20b564d9b961f657d9b2bead2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>如果您喜欢视觉小说、不同的故事情节并对游戏告诉您的一切保持近乎持续的警惕，那么<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/paranormasight-the-seven-mysteries-of-honjo-switch/">《Paranormasight》</a>将是一次疯狂的旅程。<em>超自然视觉：本庄七大谜团</em>将九个（别问）日本民间故事、灵魂、诅咒和浮世绘联系在一起。完成教程式的第一个故事后，您将在多个角色之间跳转，尽管您将不可避免地返回到这个故事以寻找线索和提示。甚至演示风格也符合日本暮光之城的氛围。这些插图有磨损的红色、蓝色和绿色轮廓，模仿旧电视。你将面对其他拥有致命诅咒力量的人，造成动漫式的对峙，你要么试图溜出危险，要么让其他诅咒者落入你的陷阱。最终，这一切都得出了一个明智的结论，我们希望未来还会有更多的<em>超自然视觉</em>章节。 <em>— 马特·史密斯，英国分社社长</em></p><h2><strong>银河战士 Prime 重制版</strong></h2><p><core-commerce id="12f15f71405941a88b356335e880279d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcsTIIYT_EzC1pZtCiFpztOIDJvX5U3eD0K2v2Slvr9q&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09YZNRQ7S%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B09YZNRQ7S/ref=ox_sc_act_title_1?smid=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;psc=1" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>银河战士 Prime 重制版</em></a><em>&nbsp;</em>对任天堂最伟大的游戏之一进行了现代化改造，彻底修改了其模型、纹理和高清灯光（同时保持锁定的 60 fps），并添加了更舒适的双摇杆控制方案。除此之外，它不会影响核心游戏，这是一件非常好的事情。 <em>《银河战士 Prime》</em>仍然是一款氛围方面的杰作，它捕捉到了通过别人的眼睛遇到外星世界的奇妙和孤独。虽然赏金猎人萨姆斯·阿兰（Samus Aran）有一些战斗，但这更像是第一人称探索游戏，而不是第一人称射击游戏。大约 20 年过去了，放慢脚步，领略 Tallon IV 世界的细节仍然令人着迷。 <em>— Jeff Dunn，高级商业作家</em></p><h2><strong>卡比与被遗忘的土地</strong></h2><p><core-commerce id="507a12ab64cf4b6bb9af3d3544e933af" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9LaXJieS1hbmQtdGhlLUZvcmdvdHRlbi1MYW5kL2RwL0IwOVJNTUJaQlI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHAtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjRjOWVhNzc3LTI0YzItNDRiZS05MzZkLWJkNWE1NDQzNWNjZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAARaSlNh6Z9nrYBIn5GPweF6Zh2rAiT1QQlXH4-qJudgK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FKirby-and-the-Forgotten-Land%2Fdp%2FB09RMMBZBR" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>《卡比与被遗忘的土地》</em></a>将任天堂可爱的粉红色斑点带入了 3D 世界。它的结构远没有<em>《超级马里奥奥德赛》</em>开放和流畅，但游戏在精神上同样有趣。最重要的是“口模式”，卡比吞咽并呈现某些物体的形状以通过特定的阶段。除了简单地有趣之外——享受“杯垫嘴卡比”或“螺栓存储嘴卡比”——这种重新利用普通材料并呈现新感觉的方式是令人愉快的。 “烟斗嘴卡比”将一根烟斗变成一个滚动的破坏圆筒，“水气球嘴卡比”将你变成一个巨大的摇晃的物体，等等。虽然它在最后开始回收，但游戏的大部分内容都以经典的任天堂方式展示了新的想法。虽然这个故事不是普利策奖的作品，但它的结局却非常荒谬。和大多数<em>《星之卡比》</em>游戏一样，它对于所有技能水平的人来说都足够轻松，但在默认难度下却不是那么容易。 — 京东</p><h2>星界链</h2><p><core-commerce id="d532dd2dcbf64e8cace66334cbdaabf9" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>从第一部预告片发布那天起，直到我玩了几个小时，我对<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Bc3RyYWwtQ2hhaW4tTmludGVuZG8tU3dpdGNoL2RwL0IwN05RRjc0TTM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHAtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjRjOWVhNzc3LTI0YzItNDRiZS05MzZkLWJkNWE1NDQzNWNjZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAR3jcHvEHVPju10gNjSLwIo_zbdlzxjIKKSe76NJpQvv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAstral-Chain-Nintendo-Switch%2Fdp%2FB07NQF74M3"><em>《星界锁链》</em></a>一直持观望态度。这一切感觉有点太普通了，几乎是动作游戏的数字绘画再现。我不必如此担心，因为这是近年来来自《猎天使魔女》系列开发商 PlatinumGames 的原创游戏之一。</p><p>在未来，世界不断受到来自另一个存在位面的生物的攻击，你将扮演一支特种部队的军官来应对这种威胁。游戏的噱头是你可以驯服这些生物，使其成为你在战斗中使用的军团。在遭遇战中，你同时控制你的角色和军团，应对一波又一波的怪物和更大、更具挑战性的敌人。除了战斗之外，您还可以使用您的军团来侦破犯罪和穿越环境。</p><p> <em>《星界锁链》</em>严格遵循侦探工作、平台谜题和战斗的循环——如果我批评的话，有点太紧密了——游戏分为多个案件作为章节。这个故事开始得很好，但很快就变成了各种动漫比喻的混搭，包括直接从一些非常著名的节目和电影中摘录的曲折和弧线。然而，每分钟的游戏玩法足以让你参与 20 小时左右的主要战役，并进入相当重要的最终游戏内容。</p><p> <em>《星界锁链》</em>达到了<em>《尼尔：机械纪元》</em>的高度吗？不，一点也不，但它的战斗和环境往往可以超越那个游戏，总而言之，它可能是我这一代人中最喜欢的。如今，它的价格通常低于 50 美元，非常值得您花时间。</p><h2>塞莱斯特</h2><p><core-commerce id="57cf1e3a8f5d42dfb83f2f83299e92bd" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWFejBQXp6O_1u7hRKhOJl3hSxgiqT92BCYIIYgHmpVz&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCeleste-Nintendo-Switch-Digital-Code%2Fdp%2FB079Z1LPSP"><em>塞莱斯特</em></a>有很多东西。这是一款很棒的平台游戏，同时也是一款益智游戏。这是极其惩罚性的，但也很容易实现。它把游戏玩法置于一切之上，但它有一个很棒的故事。这是一款美丽、感人且令人难忘的矛盾游戏，由 MattMakesGames（出色的<em>《Towerfall》</em>背后的独立工作室）制作。因此，无论您拥有什么平台， <em>《Celeste》</em>都值得购买，但其基于房间的关卡和清晰的 2D 艺术作品使其成为一款在旅途中在 Switch 上玩的绝佳游戏。</p><h2>勇者斗恶龙 XI S：难以捉摸的时代的回声</h2><p><core-commerce id="b3adac80b0f7409c8eb0d702060692a2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9EcmFnb24tUXVlc3QtWEktRWx1c2l2ZS1EZWZpbml0aXZlLU5pbnRlbmRvL2RwL0IwN05RR0RYUlk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHAtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjRjOWVhNzc3LTI0YzItNDRiZS05MzZkLWJkNWE1NDQzNWNjZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAATtEkVVMJKVpot09mb9yKTD4LQufirePuQJHccNZsP8L&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDragon-Quest-XI-Elusive-Definitive-Nintendo%2Fdp%2FB07NQGDXRY"><em>《勇者斗恶龙 XI》</em></a>是一款毫不掩饰的传统日本角色扮演游戏。大多数角色都是既定的角色扮演游戏比喻：沉默的主角（实际上是传奇英雄）、法师姐妹、神秘的盗贼等等。然后是战斗系统，该系统在该系列的数十年中很少发生变化。 （这个特别版采用 16 位风格的游戏版本是有原因的：在图形受限的环境中，机制和故事也同样出色。）虽然故事采用了许多熟悉的 RPG 节奏，但一切都需要后来发生了有趣的转变。通过它，游戏需要完成。角色扮演游戏需要引人入胜的故事，而这款游戏正是如此。只是直到后来才完全发挥作用。</p><p>该系列的第十一次迭代也是对勇者斗恶龙所有事物的庆祝。在不深入故事的情况下，游戏大量参考了第一款游戏，发生在相同的叙事宇宙中，仅仅几百年后。</p><p> Switch 版本并没有提供最精致的游戏体验——它可以在竞争对手的游戏机上使用——但由《龙珠》成名的鸟山明设计的角色移动流畅，细节丰富，尽管混合游戏机有限制。虽然很难解释，但在任天堂游戏机上玩传统日式角色扮演游戏也有一些显而易见的<em>道理</em>。</p><h2>火焰之纹章：三座房子</h2><p><core-commerce id="55e49ecb35cf44a8a53cea800094e4e7" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcEmBmuXrAF337sijYudHXk7PJvCm_WJALON4PEQBCKN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFire-Emblem-Houses-Nintendo-Digital%2Fdp%2FB07DM7KD4W"><em>《火焰纹章：三宫》</em></a>是一款必玩的游戏。开发商Intelligent Systems对该系列在Nintendo Switch上的首次亮相的公式进行了大量调整，这些改变的结果是一款以有意义且令人满意的方式结合了《火焰纹章》双重性格的游戏。你将花费一半的时间作为一名战术大师，在各种有趣的战场上指挥部队。另一半？您将作为该国最好的学校的教授来教导学生并建立关系。</p><h2>哈迪斯</h2><p><core-commerce id="00a7ab29ed744d2d953a362013dedb95" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARN3_44YA2YDwg5CRuQcGC5oNhErQG-MNoqunBPg3PYS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHades-Limited-Nintendo-Switch%2Fdp%2FB08X2K6B1Z%2F"><em>《Hades》</em></a>是第一款进入我们最佳 PC 游戏榜单的抢先体验游戏，而最终版游戏也非常适合任天堂 Switch。这是一款由<em>Bastion</em> 、 <em>Transistor</em>和<em>Pyre</em>背后的团队开发的动作角色扮演游戏。你扮演哈迪斯的儿子扎格勒斯，他和他的父亲发生了一点口角，想要逃离冥界。为此，萨格勒斯必须从地下世​​界的各个层面杀出一条血路，直至到达地表。一路上，你会从宙斯、阿瑞斯和阿芙罗狄蒂等各种古代神灵那里获得“恩赐”，它们会对你的各种攻击产生额外的效果。每个级别都分为充满恶魔、物品和偶尔出现的小老板的房间。</p><p>由于<em>《Hades》</em>是一款“Roguelike”游戏，因此您每次都会从同一个地方开始，并且关卡会重新排列。话虽如此，您收集的物品可用于访问和升级在会话之间保留的新武器和能力。 <em>《Hades》</em>最初引起我们注意的是它的游戏玩法：你可以投入 30 分钟并尽情享受，也可以玩上几个小时。随着游戏接近最终版本，故事讲述、世界构建和总体特征才真正开始形成——有很多事情要做，有很多人要见，甚至还充满了一些浪漫。你可以玩数百个小时，但仍然能获得乐趣。</p><h2>空洞骑士</h2><p><core-commerce id="eaaa57b7bc7c41f5a4cc5c9525736c49" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>这是一款真正的热门游戏，也是为数不多的 Kickstarter 游戏之一，不仅达到了预期，而且超出了预期。 <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASK479VKqSlkjjATizIaol_0AHoFXK1ZFdFESa_HNadL&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHollow-Knight-Nintendo-Switch%2Fdp%2FB07QHXM3JY"><em>空洞骑士</em></a><em>&nbsp;</em>是一款银河恶魔城风格的2D动作冒险游戏，但也只是一种<em>心情</em>。故事发生在一片广阔、破旧的土地上，当你为你的角色（一种类似伯顿式的虫子的生物）解锁新的移动和攻击技能时，你将逐渐探索这片土地。开发人员缺乏对话和叙事，而是通过环境和氛围来传达故事，而且绝对做到了这一点。</p><p>一开始你会感到相当无力，但<em>空洞骑士</em>有一个完美的难度曲线，总是让你进步，但绝不会让事情变得容易。例如，它借用了《黑暗之魂》的机制，你需要在死亡后返回尸体以取回你的“Geo”（游戏中灵魂的替代品），这总是一个紧张的时刻。但自始至终，敌人和 NPC 都将永远令人高兴。对于一款喜怒无常的游戏来说，它有一种很好的幽默感和轻松感，主要是通过你遇到的动画和声音优美的人来体现的。鉴于其低廉的成本和极高的质量，确实没有理由不购买这款游戏。相信我们，它会赢得您的青睐。</p><h2>进入突破口</h2><p><core-commerce id="64f1e0b138b34f7b805d152637cc06b4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>回合制策略游戏什么时候不是回合制策略游戏？ <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZ6A7FscFue0kj6YIjiivOsIamIRL74fBR7IQQLGJ5pb&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FInto-Breach-Nintendo-Switch-Digital%2Fdp%2FB07H2RCLJX"><em>《Into the Breach》</em></a>是一款独立 Roguelike 游戏，您可以在其中控制机甲阻止外星人的攻击，挑战传统，并因此而变得更好。虽然它的核心机制很大程度上是《XCOM》（或者说《火焰之纹章》）的模型，但它对这些机制的作用才是如此有趣。传统的回合制策略游戏就像国际象棋游戏一样——你计划一步棋，同时预测对手会做什么，并提前思考你下一步要做什么，等等，最终目标是把他们逼到墙角并获胜。在每个<em>“Into the Breach”</em>回合开始时，游戏都会礼貌地告诉您每个敌方角色将要做<em>什么</em>、他们将在哪个方格结束以及他们将造成多少伤害。没有命中率，没有随机事件，没有运气；每个回合都是一个谜题，其中有明确的答案，告诉你如何才能取得胜利。</p><p> <em>《Into the Breach》的</em>战斗很短，而且是一款 Roguelike 游戏，其设计的可重玩性非常高。一旦你掌握了基础知识并到达终点，就会有许多不同的机甲具有新的攻击和防御机制可供学习和掌握，同时你可以混合搭配来建立你最喜欢的团队。如果您是益智游戏或回合制策略游戏的粉丝，那么这是一款必备游戏。</p><h2>塞尔达传说：荒野之息</h2><p><core-commerce id="e252425d0d8f4e2ab7465bc46c37b889" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDZXTExIWEM5P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWRwLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YzllYTc3Ny0yNGMyLTQ0YmUtOTM2ZC1iZDVhNTQ0MzVjY2YifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAbqryi76xo7iqi0OSiZFdJ2qtoRw36MWbouVYggK6l2N&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB06WLLHXC9"><em>《塞尔达传说：荒野之息》</em></a>标志着该系列自任天堂 64 版<em>《时之笛》</em>以来最大的转变，它很可能是过去十年中最好的游戏之一。它将长期运行的系列引入现代游戏，具有完美的难度曲线和令人难以置信的开放世界。这里有制作工艺、会退化的武器，几乎太多的东西需要收集和制作，还有一个隐藏的温柔故事供玩家自己发现。即使没有有趣的 DLC 附加组件，这里也有很多事情要做，并且适合各个级别的玩家挑战。</p><h2>塞尔达传说：王国之泪</h2><p><core-commerce id="3a86e38b6f014cbaae275034229b64a0" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWPjwUrgyhi8sycGkwFARF9PiunQPeZyJve7bTveeitj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLegend-Zelda-Kingdom-Standard-Nintendo%2Fdp%2FB0BX854JYZ%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>《塞尔达传说：荒野之息》</em></a>是对任天堂最受尊敬的系列游戏之一的疯狂改造，没过多久，该公司就宣布正在制作直接续作。最终的结果是<em>《王国之泪》</em> ，一款以一些完全意想不到的方式重新混合<em>BotW 的</em>游戏。你仍在探索海拉鲁，几乎可以前往你能看到的任何地点，并且仍然有数十个小神殿需要清除，还有更大的任务你可以按照你喜欢的顺序完成。</p><p>但还有一个广阔的地下世界以及一个充满岛屿的神秘天空世界可供探索，这些新的地点提供了与你在海拉尔发现的不同的新挑战和危险。林克拥有多项新技能可以让他占据上风，其中包括超手。这让你可以抓住几乎任何东西并将其粘贴到其他物体上，让你可以建造各种装置，无论是实用的还是荒谬的。 《Ultrahand》为你在游戏中遇到的每个谜题提供了各种各样的解决方案，当你找到正确的解决方案来解决阻碍你的问题时，你会比过去的《塞尔达传说》游戏更令人满意。 <em>《王国之泪》</em>继承了<em>《荒野之息》</em>的所有优点，并将其提升到了一个新的水平。 <em>— 内森·英格拉汉姆，副主编</em></p><h2><strong>极乐迪斯科最终剪辑</strong></h2><p><core-commerce id="27165816738e43e39828b0852bfc046e" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQSloMMKVvqLiBVAHQD0T2YxWtZgpQ9TCSdEvIjiECHm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDisco-Elysium-Final-Cut-Nintendo-Switch%2Fdp%2FB09P4CH1FB"><em>极乐迪斯科</em></a>是一款特殊的游戏。这是爱沙尼亚工作室 ZA/UM 的第一款作品，是一款庞大的科幻角色扮演游戏，与现代战斗游戏相比，它更多地从《龙与地下城》和<em>《博德之门》</em>中汲取灵感。事实上，没有战斗可言，相反，你将创建你的角色，选择他们的优点和缺点，然后通过 D&amp;D 风格的技能检查来完成故事。当然，你会通过物品来提升你的能力并提升统计数据，但实际上游戏的系统已经消失，取而代之的是一个真正引人入胜的故事，其中包括一些有史以来最精美的文字，为电子游戏增光添彩。</p><p>在原作 18 个月后发布的<em>《最终剪辑》</em>中，这款对话极其丰富的游戏现在拥有完整的配音，这比以往任何时候都更加生动地呈现了这个独特的世界。 <em>Final Cut</em>在 PC、PS5 和 Stadia 上首次亮相后，现在可用于所有现有的家用游戏机 - 包括任天堂的 Switch。加载时间比其他系统要慢一些，因此它可能不是绝对最好的播放平台，但<em>极乐迪斯科</em>是一种与 Switch 库的其他游戏不同的体验，这就是它进入此列表的原因。</p><h2>马里奥赛车 8 豪华版</h2><p><core-commerce id="29c5415c5cf247ad95062c889f9b697a" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9NYXJpby1LYXJ0LURlbHV4ZS1OaW50ZW5kby1EaWdpdGFsL2RwL0IwMU4xMDM3Q1Y_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHAtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjRjOWVhNzc3LTI0YzItNDRiZS05MzZkLWJkNWE1NDQzNWNjZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAW8YM_F6RFQfAdeTnF8fGsF8NAwrfCWh1NDrqu6ew53s&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMario-Kart-Deluxe-Nintendo-Digital%2Fdp%2FB01N1037CV"><em>《马里奥赛车 8 豪华版》的</em></a>活力和对细节的关注证明它是 Wii U 原版的有效升级。角色在赛跑时生动可爱，任天堂制作了更大、更宽的赛道，最多可容纳 12 名赛车手。此版本的《马里奥赛车》包括反重力悬停轮胎和自动滑翔机，当您冲出坡道时，让比赛在视觉上更加刺激，但其核心是《马里奥赛车》——简单、纯粹的游戏乐趣。它还很好地展示了 Switch 所具有的多种游戏模式：任何地方都可以进行两人分屏游戏，就像在线比赛或 Switch-on-Switch 混乱一样。目前，这是最终版本。</p><h2>奥利奥利世界</h2><p><core-commerce id="aa3103dc98a544359fdf44c01e791e7d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <em>OlliOlli</em>及其续集<em>《OlliOlli 2：欢迎来到 Olliwood》</em>是出了名的难以掌握。他们令人恼火，但当你完成了获得高分所需的正确技巧和磨练组合时，也会感到非常满意。</p><p>我担心<a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9PbGxpT2xsaS1Xb3JsZC1TdGFuZGFyZC1OaW50ZW5kby1EaWdpdGFsL2RwL0IwOVYyUlY3TFc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHAtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjRjOWVhNzc3LTI0YzItNDRiZS05MzZkLWJkNWE1NDQzNWNjZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAbRNhTh9XzjYLJZkSQ2lYbrU5Lcne8UlUtk1Ij_riHRH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOlliOlli-World-Standard-Nintendo-Digital%2Fdp%2FB09V2RV7LW"><em>OlliOlli World</em></a>丰富多彩且受欢迎的系列新方向会消除这种程度的挑战，但我不应该担心。开发商 Roll7 制作了一款比原版游戏明显更平易近人的游戏，但对于那些渴望这些游戏的人来说，它保持了抽搐反应游戏玩法和分数追逐的高点完整。</p><p>很难总结到底是什么让<em>《OlliOlli World》</em>如此引人注目，但这款游戏将严峻的挑战与让你真正进入难以捉摸的心流状态的时刻混合在一起，在这种状态下，你只需施展技巧，沿着轨道行驶，通常会在没有任何刺激的情况下冲过赛道。对自己正在做的事情想得太多。音乐、音效、艺术风格、关卡设计和各种动作都营造出这种氛围——尽管游戏看起来与前作完全不同，但最终的结果是一样的：滑板的幸福。</p><h2>超级马里奥 3D 世界 + 库巴之怒</h2><p><core-commerce id="4dbadf7812464dcbba2aa6c139e51179" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARXXJoTVtkNmLtCudO6r_x5ITfcqG3hm0igXTYdBnGUH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSuper-Mario-3D-World-Bowsers-Fury%2Fdp%2FB08JCZKTQW"><em>超级马里奥 3D 世界</em></a><em>&nbsp;</em> 2013 年首次推出时，它受到了不公平的关注，主要是因为很少有人拥有 Wii U。它是老式复古马里奥机制到 3D 的绝佳翻译（<em>马里奥 64</em>是一部杰作，是的，但除非你&#39;作为一款速跑游戏，它的节奏不及 NES 和 SNES 游戏）。这也是一款很棒的多人游戏，因为你可以与其他三名玩家一起玩合作模式，并通过关卡进行比赛——每个关卡的获胜者都可以在下一个关卡中戴上王冠。</p><p>随着转向 Switch，任天堂终于开始涉足在线游戏，你现在可以远程进行游戏，这是一个巨大的优势。更大的补充是<em>《Bowser&#39;s Fury》</em> ，这是一款全新的游戏，玩起来更像是<em>《超级马里奥奥德赛》</em>和<em>《3D 世界》的混合体。</em>有一些非常有创意的挑战，感觉就像来自<em>《奥德赛》</em> ，与 Wii U 游戏的轻盈和速度融为一体。 （应该指出的是，与主游戏不同， <em>《Bowser&#39;s Fury》</em>也只适合一到两个玩家。）我们推荐<em>3D World</em>单独使用，但作为与<em>《Bowser&#39;s Fury》的套装，</em>它会变得更划算。</p><h2>超级马里奥奥德赛</h2><p><core-commerce id="5739b4bc9255480a95983abe6815034a" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXw-FHdr-Y2SRpbBsHQF2m9yxlHshmkmrMS3o_D79zBp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSuper-Mario-Odyssey-Nintendo-Digital%2Fdp%2FB072KG45JD"><em>《超级马里奥奥德赛》</em></a>可能并不代表<em>《荒野之息》</em>对《塞尔达传说》系列的重大改变，但它是一款伟大的马里奥游戏，在过去二十年里不断完善。 Yes, we got some important modern improvements, like maps and fast travel, and the power-stealing Cappy is a truly fun addition to Mario&#39;s usual tricks. But that core joy of Mario, figuring out the puzzles, racing to collect items and exploring landmarks, is here in abundance.</p><h2> Super Smash Bros. Ultimate </h2><p><core-commerce id="2642af93071b4037ad942d8add738d88" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> This is the ultimate distillation of Nintendo&#39;s multiplayer fighting game. The series&#39; debut on Switch brings even more characters from beyond Nintendo&#39;s stable. If you&#39;re sick of Mario, Pikachu and Metroid&#39;s Samus, perhaps <em>Final Fantasy VII</em> &#39;s Cloud, Solid Snake or Bayonetta will be your new go-to character. There are about 80 characters to test out here (although 10 of them are locked behind DLC).</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAenCRbEIi5oXDPq0wplecE47mLr-yOd2eU38dX9NtUQe&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSuper-Smash-Bros-Ultimate-Nintendo-Switch%2Fdp%2FB07DMFRNF9%3F"><em>Super Smash Bros. Ultimate</em></a> features a divisive new single-player mode where you augment characters with stickers, battling through special conditions to unlock more characters and, yes, more stickers. At its core, Smash Bros. games combine fast-paced, chaotic fights with an incredibly beginner-friendly learning curve. Yes, some items are confusing or overpowered, but your special moves are only a two-button combination away. Turning the tables is built into the DNA of <em>Super Smash Bros. Ultimate</em> , ensuring thrilling battles (once you&#39;ve sorted handicaps) for everyone involved.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-nintendo-switch-games-160029843.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-nintendo-switch-games-160029843.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4c9ea777-24c2-44be-936d-bd5a54435ccf</guid><dc:creator> Engadget</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 21 Aug 2023 18:35:53 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692642954</ingested><modified> 2023-08-21T18:36:08+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Engadget]]></category><media:content height="883" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-05/e80b9d40-b40a-11eb-97f3-676e1398a862" width="1549"><media:keywords> headline </media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="883" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-05/e80b9d40-b40a-11eb-97f3-676e1398a862" width="1549"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A light blue Nintendo Switch sits upside down on a coffee table.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Nintendo Switch]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The cozy cat game that escaped from Valve]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Imagine a game that might be described as the opposite of <em>Half-Life 2</em> , <em>Left 4 Dead</em> or <em>Counter-Strike: Global Offensive</em> .这些是第一人称射击游戏，背景设定在饱受战争蹂躏的后世界末日城市，所以它们的反面可能是一款完全没有武器的第三人称游戏，背景设定在一个温暖、热闹的大都市，里面有友好的角色，主角可能是一只可爱的猫。 Weirdly, the result could look a lot like <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> , the first project from former Valve designer Matt T. Wood.</p><p> In nearly 17 years at Valve, Wood helped build and ship the company&#39;s most notable titles, including <em>Left 4 Dead</em> , <em>Left 4 Dead 2</em> , <em>Portal 2,</em> <em>CS:GO</em> and both episodes of <em>Half-Life 2</em> . He was a founding member of the <em>CS:GO</em> project and worked on that series for six years; he was pivotal in crafting <em>Portal 2</em> ’s co-op mode, and he created choreography and combat scenes in Half-Life and Left 4 Dead. Level design was one of his specialties.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Wood left Valve in mid-2019, and today he&#39;s the head of his own game development company in Seattle, Washington, Double Dagger Studio. He didn&#39;t plan on starting his own studio post-Valve, and he certainly didn&#39;t think he&#39;d be building and self-publishing a game about an adorable cat. But, he is, and it&#39;s called <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> .</p><p> “It really is more about cozy exploration,” Wood told Engadget. “The game has aspects of platforming, but it&#39;s very light platforming.更多的是垂直探索，探索角落和缝隙。 I&#39;ve done a lot of things throughout my career, but one of the things I spent a lot of time doing was level design in video games, so I have a lot of personal interest in creating spaces that feel fun to explore, to sort of poke around in.” </p><div id="d1712f3d32114b4eba73f62b468c001c"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dB6eEYtfVsw?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p> <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> has Saturday-morning-cartoon vibes, with hand-animated scenes and a clean, friendly art style. The main character, Kitty, has wide green eyes, inky fur and batlike ears, and they&#39;re on a mission to find their way home to an apartment complex in the center of a bustling downtown.然而，拖延是受到高度鼓励的。 <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> is an open-world game filled with adorable animals to befriend, people to pester, quests to complete and hats to wear.</p><p> The hats are embellished bonnets that come in various forms, including a fish head, a half-shucked corn cob, little devil ears, a cowboy situation, a hedgehog and even some root vegetables. Kitty&#39;s face endearingly pokes through the center of each hat, and they can be equipped at will throughout the game. Aside from a few unique cases, there are no stats attached to the hats — wearing the ladybug head doesn&#39;t grant Kitty movement speed, and the construction hat doesn&#39;t add bonus armor. Mostly, they exist to be cute.</p><p> “As a game designer, you kind of sit down and go, what is the purpose of this thing that you&#39;re doing?”伍德说道。 “You always need a function, a purpose, a reason for doing the thing.我想十年前，我会说，好吧，帽子会给你这种能力，或者，就像，所有的游戏玩法都会与所有这些东西联系在一起。虽然帽子的某些方面确实如此，但很大程度上，它们只是装饰性的。 It was refreshing to come to that conclusion to say, no, these are just for fun.” </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/6a562430-4047-11ee-bffb-74ae840d35a8" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/6a562430-4047-11ee-bffb-74ae840d35a8" style="height:1080px;width:1920px;" alt="小猫咪，大城市" data-uuid="8239f8bf-9d87-372e-b891-36b20094ebbb"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Double Dagger Studio</div></figure><p> Wood&#39;s long history at Valve contextualizes his current role as the founder of an independent studio, and his years inside the insular company have helped shape his approach to game design.</p><p> Valve is a unique behemoth, even in the AAA space.它拥有Steam，它的作用就像一个无底银行； it&#39;s a private company, so it doesn&#39;t have shareholders to appease; and it&#39;s the steward of iconic franchises including Portal, Half-Life, Counter-Strike, Left 4 Dead, Team Fortress and Dota 2 (many of which are on Wood&#39;s résumé).</p><p> “Valve is not a typical large game studio,” Wood said. “You have a lot of autonomy and freedom to do things there. But, you still sort of live within that direction that Valve goes in.”</p><p> Valve&#39;s internal structure has long been the subject of myth and legend among video game fans, with the company&#39;s founder Gabe Newell in the role of messiah and the Valve Handbook for New Employees as its sacred text. The handbook <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.valvesoftware.com/en/publications">made its way online</a> in 2012 and went viral for its Libertarian-inspired corporate ideals — it outlined a flat hierarchy at Valve, suggesting employees had the ability to manage themselves and work on their dream projects at any given time. This cemented Valve&#39;s reputation as an ultra-rad, super-cool <em>&nbsp;</em> video game company in the public eye, and this perception persists today.</p><p> In practice, this structure has resulted in an incredibly rich company that doesn&#39;t produce much. It&#39;s a running joke that Valve can&#39;t count to three: <em>Half-Life 2: Episode Two</em> and <em>Team Fortress 2</em> came out in 2007, <em>Left 4 Dead 2</em> came out in 2009, and <em>Portal 2</em> came out in 2011. In 2020, Valve debuted <em>Half-Life: Alyx</em> , a VR game exclusive to the studio&#39;s Index hardware, and after <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/valve-tf2-bots-crisis-video-180003369.html">ignoring an extremely disruptive bot invasion</a> , the company rolled out an update to <em>TF2</em> this summer, largely comprising community-made maps and assets. Meanwhile, Steam has been printing money while maintaining Valve&#39;s deathgrip on the PC marketplace. </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/6a589530-4047-11ee-bf6f-87f9e3e467b3" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/6a589530-4047-11ee-bf6f-87f9e3e467b3" style="height:1080px;width:1920px;" alt="小猫咪，大城市" data-uuid="6800eb64-6a7e-3cb3-8d77-e4fd6458dee9"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Double Dagger Studio</div></figure><p> When Wood talks about the fun and freedom he feels building <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> , he compares it with a top-down rigidity and complacent bureaucracy he experienced in Valve&#39;s production line. Here&#39;s how he described it:</p><p> “Valve talks a lot about, like, you can do anything you want. And it&#39;s like, well — that&#39;s never true.你知道，Valve 有一个方向，他们也有一个轨迹。因此，对我来说，我意识到 Valve 的发展方向并不是我想要长期发展的方向。 Because I&#39;d been there for a long time and they were sitting on their laurels a little bit, and it&#39;s like they weren&#39;t really challenging themselves, taking risks or doing anything. Steam&#39;s making a lot of money so they don&#39;t really have to, but I was not OK with that. And after many years of trying to figure out how to manage that, I decided, you know, it&#39;s important for me to go and make my own decisions for a while.”</p><p> Wood made it clear that he appreciated the opportunities and stability that Valve provided him, and overall he called it a “great company.” It&#39;s easy to see why so many talented game developers are drawn to Valve, a studio with unlimited resources, a laissez-faire management style and a library of prestigious IP. Working at an established studio also means there are plenty of experts around to check your progress and offer advice, and these are fail-safes that Wood doesn&#39;t have any longer as an independent developer.</p><p> “That can be a bit scary,” Wood said. “But it&#39;s been great.我喜欢与一个专注于游戏的小团队合作，对我们来说，这是不同的。 To me, it&#39;s a challenge.” </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/18f6bb30-4048-11ee-bed7-bda3f4c44af1" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/18f6bb30-4048-11ee-bed7-bda3f4c44af1" style="height:1080px;width:1920px;" alt="小猫咪，大城市" data-uuid="4eb00e16-9145-3166-9354-ae4d048107e8"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Double Dagger Studio</div></figure><p> Wood said that even though he likely works more now, he also has more energy and passion for his projects than he did in his final five years at Valve. <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> represents a litany of game-design firsts for Wood, including the fact that it&#39;s a mini open world and it has zero combat. There are now two full-time team members at Double Dagger, plus a handful of part-time developers and contributors, and they all found each other naturally, by Digital Age standards — Wood shared early ideas of <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> on Twitter, and interested creators got in touch.</p><p> “At first I did reach out to some of my co-workers who had left Valve already and they were interested, but like — this was a common theme about reaching out to people who used to work at Valve, is that most people when they leave Valve, they&#39;re kind of done,” Wood said.</p><p> Despite <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/indie-games-have-entered-the-era-of-bespoke-publishing-170639414.html">the current surge</a> of indie-focused publishers like Annapurna Interactive, Devolver Digital, Private Division, Humble, Netflix and Raw Fury, Wood is self-publishing <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> under Double Dagger Studio. That&#39;s not to say he didn&#39;t explore a potential partnership — he actually made it all the way to final contract meetings with one publisher in particular, but in the end, he turned the deal down.</p><p> “It didn&#39;t make any sense,” Wood said. “Because what they were able to do, for me, absolutely did not justify the money that they were gonna take.因此，找到一个有意义的出版商确实很难。 I think that the difference between where I was in my career, and where someone maybe right out of school would be, is that I walked away from Valve with a chunk of money that I said, &#39;I&#39;m gonna invest that into a company.&#39;因此我不必依赖发行商花费 100,000 美元进行一年的开发或其他什么。 I did have that freedom and space to say no.” </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/6a5e6190-4047-11ee-bbaf-bd22d5b8f19c" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/6a5e6190-4047-11ee-bbaf-bd22d5b8f19c" style="height:1080px;width:1920px;" alt="小猫咪，大城市" data-uuid="5cf11d1e-3981-3028-bfd4-355f5d797fa3"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Double Dagger Studio</div></figure><p> This year alone, <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> was announced for Switch, it had a successful showing at Summer Game Fest, and it&#39;s getting some fresh swag in the form of <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.makeship.com/products/little-kitty-plush">a Makeship campaign</a> offering an exceedingly cute Kitty plush and a salmon-shaped, zip-up catnip toy. The Double Dagger team is finishing the game while Wood oversees it all, no safety net in sight.</p><p> When we first started talking, Wood described <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> as something like <em>Alice in Wonderland</em> or <em>The Wizard of Oz</em> , a game about a lost soul trying to find their way home and meeting a colorful cast of characters along the journey. This may be Kitty&#39;s story, but at this stage in his career, it feels a lot like Wood&#39;s, too.</p><p> <em>Little Kitty, Big City</em> is on track to come out in 2024 for Switch and PC — <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1177980/Little_Kitty_Big_City/">via Steam</a> , of course.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/the-cozy-cat-game-that-escaped-from-valve-180052174.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-cozy-cat-game-that-escaped-from-valve-180052174.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 26dbf857-d3e9-4cd2-aad0-9629798aa545</guid><dc:creator> Jessica Conditt</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 21 Aug 2023 18:00:52 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692658982</ingested><modified> 2023-08-21T23:03:10+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Industrials]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jessica Conditt]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4a6765d0-4047-11ee-aa64-06e91b0d93f8" width="1920"><media:keywords> headline </media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4a6765d0-4047-11ee-aa64-06e91b0d93f8" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Double Dagger Studio]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Little Kitty, Big City]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Little Kitty, Big City]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Official Xbox Series X console skins are coming soon, starting with 'Starfield' and camo options]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Sony has been offering custom <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-playstation-5-console-covers-202711149.html"><ins>PlayStation 5 plates</ins></a> for quite some time now, including a recent version that brings a <em>Spider-Man 2</em> look to the console. Microsoft, which has given away several custom Xbox Series S units <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2022/05/04/win-custom-lego-star-wars-the-skywalker-saga-console/"><ins>in contests</ins></a> , is getting in on the action by selling <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2023/08/21/xbox-series-x-console-wraps-starfield-camo/"><ins>official wraps</ins></a> for the <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/xbox-series-x/"><ins>Xbox Series X</ins></a> .</p><p> Along with two camouflage colors, Arctic Camo and Mineral Camo, a <em>Starfield</em> -inspired wrap will be available. Pre-orders for <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Microsoft;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=67071605-d4df-494e-8d9c-c9c236b8bb38&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Microsoft&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASOgvwisERYSRX93mwj2OXWc-R8ucIaW8payv7KK98lI&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fd%2FXbox-Series-X-Console-Wraps%2F8x08lwws1qh7%2FNLZ4" class="rapid-with-clickid"><ins>the wraps</ins></a> are open now. The $50 <em>Starfield</em> one will ship in the US, Canada and Europe on October 18th, while the $45 camo options will hit those regions on November 10th (though fans in Europe will miss out on the Arctic option for now). </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="43dfa32ec22a4181b86025d6aa6e7377"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Prepping for some space exploration? Time to suit up! 🧑‍🚀🎮<br> ‌<br> Announcing the Xbox Series X Console Wraps are here and made to perfectly fit your console! ‌ <a href="https://t.co/KXirvvlmep">pic.twitter.com/KXirvvlmep</a></p> — Xbox (@Xbox) <a href="https://twitter.com/Xbox/status/1693654683511067059?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 21, 2023</a></blockquote></div><p> The <em>Starfield</em> wrap matches a themed controller and headset Xbox recently started selling as it gears up for its most important game of the year. Bethesda&#39;s next giant RPG <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/starfield-has-been-delayed-to-september-6th-161635848.html"><ins>drops on September 6th</ins></a> , so you&#39;ll have to wait several more weeks for the <em>Starfield</em> console wrap if you want to go all in on the game&#39;s aesthetic.</p><p> The wraps are made up of solid core panels with &quot;high-tech fabric finishes.&quot; They have a hook and loop system, as well as a silicone design on the interior, to keep them secure. Microsoft says it designed them to make sure that there was no impact on performance — the company notes that the wraps even have small feet on the bottom to help maintain airflow.</p><p> Third-party companies such as Dbrand (which previously <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/dbrand-stops-ps5-faceplate-sales-150427894.html"><ins>ran into trouble</ins></a> with Sony over its PS5 plates) have long been selling custom skins for Xbox consoles. But this isn&#39;t exactly the first time Microsoft has waded into console customization. The Xbox 360 had swappable faceplates. However, the company later <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2010-12-16-microsoft-admits-failure-with-xbox-360-faceplates-says-nobody.html"><ins>admitted this idea flopped</ins></a> . </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7688f6c0-4046-11ee-bfff-696a5b65c6ea" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7688f6c0-4046-11ee-bfff-696a5b65c6ea" style="height:1080px;width:1920px;" alt="Xbox Series X camouflage wraps. Custom skins give the console blue and grey camo looks." data-uuid="77bc8081-b322-3d04-afde-5d9c65d07641"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">微软</div></figure><p></p>This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/official-xbox-series-x-console-skins-are-coming-soon-starting-with-starfield-and-camo-options-173735898.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/official-xbox-series-x-console-skins-are-coming-soon-starting-with-starfield-and-camo-options-173735898.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3ad94791-ce59-4c52-a81b-81e83a4cb5f3</guid><dc:creator> Kris Holt</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 21 Aug 2023 17:37:35 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692639342</ingested><modified> 2023-08-21T17:36:00+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Game Consoles]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/952ff2e0-4046-11ee-bffe-c8af6ed25721" width="1920"><media:keywords> headline </media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/952ff2e0-4046-11ee-bffe-c8af6ed25721" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Microsoft]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Starfield key art and an Xbox Series X with Starfield Console Wrap]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Starfield key art and an Xbox Series X with Starfield Console Wrap]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Hard sail test hits the high seas, aiming to reduce cargo ship emissions by 30 percent]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> A cargo ship equipped with rigid sails, each the height of a 10-story building, has <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.cargill.com/2023/cargill-bar-technologies-wind-technology-sets-sail">departed</a> on its inaugural journey. The Pyxis Ocean vessel will test WindWings sails, designed to harness old-school air power to help reduce fuel usage — and the shipping industry&#39;s CO2 emissions. The sail&#39;s creators estimate the technology could decarbonize cargo ships by about 30 percent as the maritime sector tries to reach net-zero emissions by 2050. The estimated reduction could be higher if paired with alternative fuels.</p><p> The ship has been retrofitted with two WindWings, each measuring 37.5 m (123 ft) tall. The rigid sails are made from the same materials as wind turbines and can be added to cargo ships&#39; decks, providing an option for older vessels to reduce environmental impact. The ship&#39;s maiden voyage will chart a route from China to Brazil.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> The project is a collaboration between BAR Technologies (which developed the sails), Cargill Ocean Transportation, Mitsubishi Corporation and Yara Marine. “The Maritime Industry is an extremely hard industry to decarbonize,” said Cargill president Jan Dieleman. “So there&#39;s not many tools that you have. So it&#39;s really important that we as users of the maritime industry are also going to get involved in some of the innovation and really move the industry forward.” </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/d9693a90-4044-11ee-9957-f48f6005aff3" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/d9693a90-4044-11ee-9957-f48f6005aff3" style="height:1440px;width:2560px;" alt="一艘装有两个巨大而坚硬的帆的货船。从其中一张帆的顶部附近俯视下来的鸟瞰图（在船的大部分甲板上都可以看到这两张帆）。" data-uuid="cd321ec3-60dd-3d62-93ec-518dc133b77d"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> BAR Technologies</div></figure><p> The shipping industry agreed in July to reduce its greenhouse gas emissions to net zero “by or around, ie, close to, 2050.” The nonbinding agreement is essentially toothless but meant as a signal to governments of where to benchmark their (binding) targets, <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/06/climate/cargo-ship-emissions-agreement.html">according to</a> <em>The New York Times</em> . The agreement would have been even more lax if not for a “strong last-minute push” from small island nations and other less economically developed coastal countries, which led to a plan that provides a chance at limiting global warming to 1.5 degrees Celsius. That&#39;s the threshold climate experts agree the world needs to avoid to <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-10-08-major-un-report-climate-change-worse.html">spare Earth from the worst climate-change scenarios</a> .</p><p> “We fought tooth and nail for these numbers,” Carlos Fuller, Belize&#39;s representative at the United Nations, told the <em>NYT</em> last month. “They aren&#39;t perfect, but they give us a shot at staying within 1.5 degrees Celsius. And that&#39;s what we came here to do.”</p><p> Wind power has the potential to help reach those goals, but adoption is a challenge. “We have the number of ships using this technology doubling over the past 12 months,” Stephen Gordon, managing director at maritime data firm Clarksons Research, <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-66543643">told</a> the <em>BBC</em> . “This is from a low base, however. In the international shipping fleet and new-build order book of over 110,000 vessels, we have records for under 100 having wind-assisted technology today.” </p><div id="58dafc57546d4d0285128ac9983d0c30"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KNZlQXBvQCk" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/hard-sail-test-hits-the-high-seas-aiming-to-reduce-cargo-ship-emissions-by-30-percent-172738236.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/hard-sail-test-hits-the-high-seas-aiming-to-reduce-cargo-ship-emissions-by-30-percent-172738236.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 20be6b10-c7b3-4014-9882-d8eca91ed373</guid><dc:creator> Will Shanklin</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 21 Aug 2023 17:27:38 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692638859</ingested><modified> 2023-08-21T17:27:44+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nature & Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1440" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/71073bb0-4043-11ee-9f7f-8f3a837da63a" width="2560"><media:keywords> headline </media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1440" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/71073bb0-4043-11ee-9f7f-8f3a837da63a" width="2560"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[BAR Technologies]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A cargo ship fitted with two giant (white-colored) rigid sails floats on the open sea. The enormous ship has reddish sides and white-ish deck.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Pyxis Ocean cargo ship]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[YouTube wants to benefit from AI-generated music without the copyright headaches]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> YouTube is quickly becoming a home for <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ai-generated-music-wont-win-a-grammy-anytime-soon-211855194.html">AI-generated music</a> , and the service is trying to strike a balance between the technology&#39;s fans and the labels eager to protect their copyrights. The company and partners like Universal Music Group (UMG) have <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://blog.youtube/inside-youtube/partnering-with-the-music-industry-on-ai/">unveiled</a> a set of principles for AI music. In theory, the approach encourages adoption while keeping artists paid.</p><p> To start, YouTube maintains that &quot;AI is here&quot; and that it must have a &quot;responsible&quot; strategy. Accordingly, it&#39;s forming a Music AI Incubator that will influence the company&#39;s strategy. UMG and artists it represents (including Rosanne Cash, Yo Gotti and Frank Sinatra&#39;s estate) will help gather insights from YouTube&#39;s AI experiments.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> YouTube also says AI music must include &quot;appropriate protections&quot; against copyright violations, and must also provide &quot;opportunities&quot; for partners who want to get involved. While the video giant hasn&#39;t detailed what this will entail, it suggests it will build on the Content ID system that helps rights holders flag their material. On top of this, YouTube claims it will scale its content policies and safety structure to adapt to AI. The firm already has systems in place to catch copyright abuse, misinformation and other violations, but intends to pour more resources into those methods.</p><p> The principles are currently vague and don&#39;t do much to change YouTube&#39;s stance. More details are due in the months ahead, however, including policies, particular technologies and monetization for creators.</p><p> Generative AI is increasingly popular for unauthorized collaborations and mashups (including for UMG artists <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/copyright-in-spotlight-after-streaming-platforms-pull-ai-generated-drake-song-183513972.html">like Drake</a> and Frank Sinatra), but it&#39;s also finding legitimate uses. The surviving members of The Beatles are using AI to create a &#39;final&#39; song <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/paul-mccartney-is-using-ai-to-create-a-final-song-for-the-beatles-133839244.html">from a John Lennon recording</a> , while electronic artist Holly Herndon <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/holly-plus-holly-herndon-dolly-parton-jolene-ai-cover-204750236.html">covered Dolly Parton</a> using an AI voice. UMG itself is exploring <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/universal-music-group-partners-with-endel-for-ai-generated-wellness-soundscapes-183951335.html">AI-made soundscapes</a> . YouTube&#39;s principles could help it profit from legal productions while dodging lawsuits from artists and labels worried about ripoffs.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/youtube-wants-to-benefit-from-ai-generated-music-without-the-copyright-headaches-162247510.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/youtube-wants-to-benefit-from-ai-generated-music-without-the-copyright-headaches-162247510.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3bfcb49d-a65f-4d36-b101-33aed3f574ce</guid><dc:creator> Jon Fingas</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 21 Aug 2023 16:22:47 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692636612</ingested><modified> 2023-08-21T16:50:15+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Social & Online Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7f4cf110-4034-11ee-bf76-171e641c3b00" width="6000"><media:keywords> headline </media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7f4cf110-4034-11ee-bf76-171e641c3b00" width="6000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Headph